nodes.text: "BountyH" was the online alias of a Bounty Hunter who lived on Tatooine. By 0 BBY, BountyH visited Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina, and thought that the food wasn't the best, however BountyH also thought that the establishment's lighting was handy for secret meetings. BountyH posted a three-star review of the cantina in Yoda's Guide to the Galaxy, a book written by the Jedi Master Yoda during his exile on Dagobah.
BountyH was first mentioned in the 2021 non-canon reference book LEGO Star Wars Yoda's Galaxy Atlas.
